00:18:57.048 --> 00:18:58.128
Virat..

00:18:59.608 --> 00:19:00.568
Terima kasih IBU.

00:19:00.972 --> 00:19:03.292
Anda selalu mendukung kami.

00:19:06.211 --> 00:19:08.091
Terima kasih.
