00:19:11.297 --> 00:19:12.377
Sai?

00:19:15.380 --> 00:19:18.180
Ibu dan tante adalah..

00:19:20.808 --> 00:19:22.448
Mereka sedikit ortodoks.

00:19:24.408 --> 00:19:26.648
Apapun yang baru saja ibu katakan

